    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "但Frank在日记里写得很清楚——'去Moore银行借钱'。他以为自己是从一家正规银行借款。他根本不知道Moore投资公司是什么东西。",
    "enWords": "But Frank wrote it plainly in his diary — 'went to Moore Bank to borrow money.' He believed he was borrowing from a legitimate bank. He had no idea what Moore Investment Company even was.",
