    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "客户对法律实体的理解不是我的责任。协议上白纸黑字写的是Moore投资公司。他签了字——这就是同意。",
    "enWords": "The client's understanding of legal entities is not my responsibility. The agreement clearly states Moore Investment Company in black and white. He signed it — that constitutes consent.",
