    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "他没签——是Leonard代签的，你忘了？但关键不在这里。关键是你的手法：用银行的招牌吸引借款人走进门——然后把贷款转到一家不受银行法监管的壳公司名下。",
    "enWords": "He didn't sign — Leonard did, remember? But that's not the point. The point is your method: you use the bank's name and reputation to lure borrowers through the door — then route the loan through a shell company outside banking regulations.",
