    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "银行法限制利率上限，所以你用Moore投资公司来绕开监管。月息百分之二十四、利滚利、百分之百的管理费——这些条款放在银行里根本不可能通过审计。但换一个马甲，就没人管了。",
    "enWords": "Banking law caps interest rates, so you use Moore Investment Company to circumvent regulation. Twenty-four percent monthly, compound interest, a hundred-percent admin fee — these terms would never survive a bank audit. But put on a different hat, and nobody's watching.",
    "next": "230028",
