    "enSpeaker": "Harold Moore",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "这...这些都是合法的商业结构。投资公司有权自行设定条款。你可以去问任何一个律师——",
    "enWords": "This... these are all legitimate business structures. An investment company has the right to set its own terms. You can ask any lawyer —",
