    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "让我把整件事串起来。Frank走进你的银行，你的员工帮他办了一笔他根本没签字的贷款——利率是正常银行的几十倍，通过一家壳公司放出去。然后当他还不起钱的时候，你派打手上门催收。",
    "enWords": "Let me put it all together. Frank walked into your bank, your employee processed a loan he never signed — at rates dozens of times higher than a normal bank, routed through a shell company. Then when he couldn't repay, you sent enforcers to his door.",
