    "cnWords": "等一下——等一下。Brennan先生，我们冷静一下。你说得对，我承认贷款条款确实...激进了一些。但我绝对没有杀人。",
    "enWords": "Wait — wait. Mr. Brennan, let's calm down. You're right, I admit the loan terms were... aggressive. But I absolutely did not kill anyone.",
